channel.title: If your Pc crashes can it
channel.description:
The mother board on the PC my server was running is failed. Luckily I was able to get it back on to transfer the server files to another but now a lot of the shit is messed up. for example; the commands arent working, when people donate 5 dollars for a staff of light it gives them 2 everytime they log in DX.
Is this possible or were the files messed with?
